# VEHICLE::SET_CARGOBOB_PICKUP_ROPE_TYPE

## Summary
Set what kind of pick-up rope gadget the cargobob will have when deployed

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** cargobob
* **PICKUP_GADGET_TYPE** type
